Strictly Come Dancing star Giovanni Pernice took to Instagram today to congratulate Lauren Oakley as she was confirmed as one of the BBC One show’s latest additions. In a heartwarming picture shared in view of his 802,000 followers, Giovanni could be seen hugging and kissing Lauren on the cheek. Meanwhile, Lauren smiled for the camera as snapped a mirror selfie of the pair. Taking to his Instagram Stories, Giovanni wrote: "Nobody deserves it more than you @laurenmayoakley [heart emoji]… go on super [star]."